        <title type="html"><![CDATA[【保姆级教程】使用Gridea搭博客，小白也能轻松上号！]]></title>
        <id>http://iguangdie-me.ml/post/shi-yong-gridea-da-bo-ke-xiao-bai-ye-neng-qing-song-shang-hao/</id>
        <link href="http://iguangdie-me.ml/post/shi-yong-gridea-da-bo-ke-xiao-bai-ye-neng-qing-song-shang-hao/">
        </link>
        <updated>2021-02-27T00:14:14.000Z</updated>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>带家好啊，大家应该有发现我用的是Github Pages搭的博客<br>
<strong>“Github Pages？写文章不是要累死人哦”</strong><br>
那也不是，Gridea是一个能自动生成的软件，搞得跟动态博客一样<br>
而且除了移动性之外，也非常的好用<br>
<img src="http://iguangdie-me.ml/post-images/1614384980260.png" alt="" loading="lazy"><br>
<img src="http://iguangdie-me.ml/post-images/1614385025355.png" alt="" loading="lazy"><br>
那么今天教大家怎么用Gridea上号<br>
<font size="+3">设置密钥</font><br>
<strong>注意，密钥和你的Github密码不是一个东西！！！</strong><br>
<font size="+2">1，进入设置</font><br>
<img src="http://iguangdie-me.ml/post-images/1614385083928.png" alt="" loading="lazy"><br>
<font size="+2">2，进入开发者设置</font><br>
<img src="http://iguangdie-me.ml/post-images/1614385153021.png" alt="" loading="lazy"><br>
<font size="+2">3，选择密钥</font><br>
<img src="http://iguangdie-me.ml/post-images/1614385187052.png" alt="" loading="lazy"><br>
<font size="+2">4，创建密钥</font><br>
<img src="http://iguangdie-me.ml/post-images/1614385259248.png" alt="" loading="lazy"><br>
<font size="+2">5，配置密钥</h3><br>
<strong>勾选Repo！！！</strong><br>
<img src="http://iguangdie-me.ml/post-images/1614385293562.png" alt="" loading="lazy"><br>
<font size="+2">6，获取密钥</font><br>
<font color="red" size="+2">请务必保管好你的密钥，他不会再出现第二次！！！</font><br>
<img src="http://iguangdie-me.ml/post-images/1614385384141.png" alt="" loading="lazy"><br>
<font size="+3">设置仓库</font><br>
<font size="+2">1，创建一个新的仓库</font><br>
<img src="http://iguangdie-me.ml/post-images/1614385512450.png" alt="" loading="lazy"><br>
<font size="+2">2，如图设置</font><br>
<em><em>注意：如果你有自己的域名可以不使用你的用户名.github.io，随便乱来也行，但是如果你要白嫖github的github.io域名请务必这么干，虽然说速度不会很快就是了，而且移动网也无法连接，所以说请务必整个freenom或者是买个域名，对接cloudflare，虽然说cloudflare是超级减速云，但是他都比github还要快</em><br>
<img src="http://iguangdie-me.ml/post-images/1614385598399.png" alt="" loading="lazy"><br>
<font size="+2">4，进入设置</font><br>
<img src="http://iguangdie-me.ml/post-images/1614385782874.png" alt="" loading="lazy"><br>
<font size="+2">5，配置Github Pages服务</font><br>
<img src="http://iguangdie-me.ml/post-images/1614385825258.png" alt="" loading="lazy"><br>
<img src="http://iguangdie-me.ml/post-images/1614385841383.png" alt="" loading="lazy"><br>
<img src="http://iguangdie-me.ml/post-images/1614385893412.png" alt="" loading="lazy"><br>
<font size="+3">配置你自己的域名</font><br>
<img src="http://iguangdie-me.ml/post-images/1614385934945.png" alt="" loading="lazy"><br>
在这里输入你的域名，然后你就跑去Cloudflare的DNS解析<br>
<img src="http://iguangdie-me.ml/post-images/1614386023262.png" alt="" loading="lazy"><br>
<font size="+3">配置Gridea</font><br>
<img src="http://iguangdie-me.ml/post-images/1614386127162.png" alt="" loading="lazy"><br>
<img src="http://iguangdie-me.ml/post-images/1614386133421.png" alt="" loading="lazy"><br>
<br><br>
恭喜你！你已经可以开始创作了，写完文章之后点击</em><em>同步</em>*按钮就可以同步到你的github上啦！<br>
*<em>主题、Valine评论那些的不在本教程范畴</em></p>
]]></content>
